  "difficultyLevel": 5,
  "lyrics": "You should be happy sitting here in your own mind You should be happy anywhere you are, any place, anything When you're further from your own bright star Your own bright star I can't describe what you're looking at down here Looking underneath your feet Wondering if you've lost everything around you Oh, I know that I'm never coming down as long as you're around Now I know I'm never gonna come down as long as you're around From the seas up to the valley To the windows of the clouds To the peaks of the mountain and the mountain and the soldiers No, I'm never coming down Yo, I'm never coming down I'm never coming down No, no, no, I'm never coming down When everything's gone lost inside And you know that tonight you're rocking too high Just bag it right, rock it right, take a night Take a little stroll inside your mind tonight When it gets dark, you know it gets brighter Unless you want to expire Don't put it out, cause I won't put it out As long as we keep climbing higher I'm never coming down Ooh, yeah I'm never coming down You're never coming down As long as you come around with me Around again, around the bend and not touch the end Don't put a false start on a false bravado Don't make it the end of the scenery Just dream with me and never come down Oh, yeah I'm never coming down Just dream, just be with me And never, never, never come around As long as you're around, I'm never coming down I swear I've been found I believe in me, believe in scenery Believe in ecstasy, believe in all inside me I'm never coming down with you again So if you wanna fly around then jump down Jump off here, jump off the ledge I'll watch as you fly away Cause you're taking advice and you're taking them The better way for you, you can only know You can only know which way is better for The lights above me I'm never coming down from the lights above me I see that star, I see that moment Repeating a spark in history Don't you know I own that shit Thanks for watching!",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 6.179999828338623,
      "text": "You should be happy sitting here in your own mind",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 11.4399995803833,
      "text": "You should be happy anywhere you are, any place, anything",
      "start": 6.579999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 14.800000190734863,
      "text": "When you're further from your own bright star",
      "start": 11.4399995803833
    },
    {
      "end": 18.81999969482422,
      "text": "Your own bright star",
      "start": 15.920000076293945
    },
    {
      "end": 21.860000610351562,
      "text": "I can't describe what you're looking at down here",
      "start": 18.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 23.520000457763672,
      "text": "Looking underneath your feet",
      "start": 21.860000610351562
    },
    {
      "end": 26.8799991607666,
      "text": "Wondering if you've lost everything around you",
      "start": 23.520000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 33.52000045776367,
      "text": "Oh, I know that I'm never coming down as long as you're around",
      "start": 26.8799991607666
    },
    {
      "end": 39.7599983215332,
      "text": "Now I know I'm never gonna come down as long as you're around",
      "start": 33.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 42.2599983215332,
      "text": "From the seas up to the valley",
      "start": 39.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 45.900001525878906,
      "text": "To the windows of the clouds",
      "start": 42.540000915527344
    },
    {
      "end": 51.58000183105469,
      "text": "To the peaks of the mountain and the mountain and the soldiers",
      "start": 45.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 55.540000915527344,
      "text": "No, I'm never coming down",
      "start": 51.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 60.040000915527344,
      "text": "Yo, I'm never coming down",
      "start": 56.939998626708984
    },
    {
      "end": 63.36000061035156,
      "text": "I'm never coming down",
      "start": 60.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 67.05999755859375,
      "text": "No, no, no, I'm never coming down",
      "start": 63.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 70.44000244140625,
      "text": "When everything's gone lost inside",
      "start": 67.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 73.63999938964844,
      "text": "And you know that tonight you're rocking too high",
      "start": 70.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 76.81999969482422,
      "text": "Just bag it right, rock it right, take a night",
      "start": 73.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 79.72000122070312,
      "text": "Take a little stroll inside your mind tonight",
      "start": 76.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 83.26000213623047,
      "text": "When it gets dark, you know it gets brighter",
      "start": 79.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 85.5999984741211,
      "text": "Unless you want to expire",
      "start": 83.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 89.76000213623047,
      "text": "Don't put it out, cause I won't put it out",
      "start": 86.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 92.44000244140625,
      "text": "As long as we keep climbing higher",
      "start": 89.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 94.23999786376953,
      "text": "I'm never coming down",
      "start": 92.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 98.5999984741211,
      "text": "Ooh, yeah",
      "start": 96.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 100.36000061035156,
      "text": "I'm never coming down",
      "start": 98.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 103.73999786376953,
      "text": "You're never coming down",
      "start": 101.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 108.45999908447266,
      "text": "As long as you come around with me",
      "start": 103.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 113.19999694824219,
      "text": "Around again, around the bend and not touch the end",
      "start": 108.45999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 115.73999786376953,
      "text": "Don't put a false start on a false bravado",
      "start": 113.19999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 119.76000213623047,
      "text": "Don't make it the end of the scenery",
      "start": 116.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 122.95999908447266,
      "text": "Just dream with me and never come down",
      "start": 120.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 125.23999786376953,
      "text": "Oh, yeah",
      "start": 123.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 126.95999908447266,
      "text": "I'm never coming down",
      "start": 125.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 129.67999267578125,
      "text": "Just dream, just be with me",
      "start": 126.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 132.6199951171875,
      "text": "And never, never, never come around",
      "start": 129.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 136.3800048828125,
      "text": "As long as you're around, I'm never coming down",
      "start": 132.6199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 140.22000122070312,
      "text": "I swear I've been found",
      "start": 136.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 142.97999572753906,
      "text": "I believe in me, believe in scenery",
      "start": 140.22000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 146.77999877929688,
      "text": "Believe in ecstasy, believe in all inside me",
      "start": 142.97999572753906
    },
    {
      "end": 151.6199951171875,
      "text": "I'm never coming down with you again",
      "start": 146.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 155.13999938964844,
      "text": "So if you wanna fly around then jump down",
      "start": 152.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 157.5800018310547,
      "text": "Jump off here, jump off the ledge",
      "start": 155.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 162.3000030517578,
      "text": "I'll watch as you fly away",
      "start": 157.5800018310547
    },
    {
      "end": 166.25999450683594,
      "text": "Cause you're taking advice and you're taking them",
      "start": 162.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 170.1199951171875,
      "text": "The better way for you, you can only know",
      "start": 166.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 173.13999938964844,
      "text": "You can only know which way is better for",
      "start": 170.1199951171875
    },
    {
      "end": 175.5,
      "text": "The lights above me",
      "start": 173.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 180,
      "text": "I'm never coming down from the lights above me",
      "start": 176.17999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 183.3000030517578,
      "text": "I see that star, I see that moment",
      "start": 180
    },
    {
      "end": 185.39999389648438,
      "text": "Repeating a spark in history",
      "start": 183.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 188.32000732421875,
      "text": "Don't you know I own that shit",
      "start": 185.39999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 193.67999267578125,
      "text": "Thanks for watching!",
      "start": 193.60000610351562
    }
  ],
